      {
        "status": "scheduled",
        "body": "What is changing?\n\nOn 2026-04-13, we will migrate our status page to a new service provider.\n\nWhat you need to know\n\nDuring this migration:\n\n- Our status page URL will remain the same. You can access it at https://www.notion-status.com/\n- Email subscribers will be migrated to our new Status Page. No action needed.\n- RSS and Atom feeds will be available and no action needed if you are subscribed via the notion-status.com URL.\n\nWhat you need to do\n\n - Email subscribers will be automatically migrated. No action is required.\n - We are providing the maintenance notice for awareness.\n\nIf you need assistance or have any questions, please contact our support team at team@makenotion.com.",
